  "all_platforms": false,
  "all_platforms_descr": "Origin Trial support: ChromeOS, Windows, Mac and Linux.\n\nLaunch support: Initially planned for ChromeOS. Windows, Mac and Linux should come later, depending on the platform-related issues.\n\nThe feature is not planned for Android and Android WebView because they don't usually feature the traditional windows found on desktop platforms.",
